  EffectDiscription_JPN: 
  EffectDiscription_ENG: '[Start of Your Main Phase] By returning this Tamer to the
    bottom of the deck, you may play 1 [Owen Dreadnought] from your hand without
    paying the cost. Then, if you don''t have a Digimon, you may play 1 [Elizamon]
    from your trash without paying the cost.

    [Your Turn] When any of your Digimon
    digivolve into a [Reptile] or [Dragonkin] Digimon, by suspending this Tamer,
    that Digimon gets +3000 DP for the turn. Then, it may attack.'
